              "free_text": [
                "",
                "- By authors. It is noticeable that below 34 MeV, the",
                "measurements of Mukherjee+ are a little lower than our",
                "measurements. The cross-sections reported by Rao+ and",
                " Michel+ are generally in agreement with ours, between",
                "34 MeV and 44 MeV, while above 44 MeV they are higher",
                "than ours. Moreover, below 34 MeV the results",
                "of Michel+ and Rao+ are exceptionally low by an order",
                "of magnitude."
              ]
